  "page": "Willam the Wanderer",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Warrior%27s_Sons\" title=\"Warrior&#39;s Sons\"><img alt=\"Warrior&#39;s Sons.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/54/Warrior%27s_Sons.svg/50px-Warrior%27s_Sons.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/54/Warrior%27s_Sons.svg/75px-Warrior%27s_Sons.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/54/Warrior%27s_Sons.svg/100px-Warrior%27s_Sons.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Willam<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Wanderer</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\"><img alt=\"Star of the Faith.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/50px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/75px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/100px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nWillam the Wanderer</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Warrior%27s_Sons\" title=\"Warrior&#39;s Sons\">Warrior's Sons</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westerosi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/42_AC\" title=\"42 AC\">42&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)<i></i></li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sons_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Sons of the Dragon\">The Sons of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Willam the Wanderer</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Warrior%27s_Sons\" title=\"Warrior&#39;s Sons\">Warrior's Sons</a> at the start of the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Willam_the_Wanderer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In <a href=\"/index.php/42_AC\" title=\"42 AC\">42&#160;AC</a>, Ser Willam was stationed at the <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> chapter of the <a href=\"/index.php/Warrior%27s_Sons\" title=\"Warrior&#39;s Sons\">Warrior's Sons</a>, based in the <a href=\"/index.php/Sept_of_Remembrance\" title=\"Sept of Remembrance\">Sept of Remembrance</a>. He fought in the <a href=\"/index.php/Trial_of_seven\" title=\"Trial of seven\">trial of seven</a> in which seven of the Warrior's Sons faced King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a> and his six champions.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Willam and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Damon_Morrigen\" title=\"Damon Morrigen\">Damon Morrigen</a> were the last Warrior's Sons standing against Maegor, whose six champions had all been killed. Badly wounded, the two were killed by Maegor with <a href=\"/index.php/Blackfyre\" title=\"Blackfyre\">Blackfyre</a>, the king's <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_steel\" title=\"Valyrian steel\">Valyrian steel</a> sword. As he fell, however, Ser Willam dealt the king a terrible blow to the head, cracking his helm and leaving him insensate. However, this was not enough to kill the king and Maegor was declared the winner.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Willam_the_Wanderer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Sons of the Dragon.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403233655\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.079 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.271 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 657/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10553/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7680/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 911/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1256/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.46 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  256.948      1 -total\n 92.58%  237.877      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 91.72%  235.681      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.08%   25.912     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  5.49%   14.100      5 Template:Infobox_label\n  4.51%   11.587      3 Template:Ref\n  3.17%    8.158      2 Template:Date\n  3.02%    7.762      3 Template:Ref/core\n  1.33%    3.428      1 Template:References\n  0.44%    1.137      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:24194-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403233655 and revision id 320734\n -->\n",
